outputs.output_descr:
UN-HABITAT/UNDP Joint Programme Output 4. GoI has improved knowledge of the potential to establish a commercial housing finance market in Iraq in line with Banking Sector Reform processes.

UNDP Output 4.1 Assessment prepared of two major state-owned commercial banks and selected private commercial banks to ascertain their position to engage in Housing Finance
